# 🔍 Attendance Management System — Deep Analysis Report

> **Date:** 02 Mar 2026 | **Scope:** Full-stack analysis | **Rating:** Against Enterprise / Studio-Grade Standards

---

## 📊 Executive Summary

| Dimension | Current | Enterprise Target | Gap |
